dcterms:dc.dc:title: Labelled weekly MR images of the male pelvis
dcterms:dc.dc:creator: Jason Dowling
dcterms:dc.dc:subject: Radiology and organ imaging
Radiation therapy
dcterms:dc.dc:description: Anonymised data in NIfTI file format. These data have been acquired as part of a retrospective MRI-alone radiation therapy study from the Calvary Mater Newcastle Hospital described in Dowling, et al. (2015), Automatic Substitute Computed Tomography Generation and Contouring for Magnetic Resonance Imaging (MRI)-Alone External Beam Radiation Therapy From Standard MRI Sequences, International Journal of Radiation Oncology*Biology*Physics, 93(5), pp. 1144-1153, https://doi.org/10.1016/j.ijrobp.2015.08.045 .
